10

Whatisionicbonding?
Isthebondingthatoccursbetweenmetalsandnon-metals.
Metalsloseelectron(s)andbecomepositivelycharged.
Non-metalsgainelectron(s)andbecomenegativelycharged.
Whatiscovalentbonding?
Isthebondingbetweennon-metals.
Allatomsshareelectrons.

Whatismetallicbonding?

fromandnegativechargeitisgoing.

Hence,articlesattractandbond.
